# Customer Research Insights

**What our customers and prospects really think**

::: warning
**Current Perceptions (Customer Interviews):**
- **"Solid but not exciting"** - 65% of responses
- **"Good value but behind the curve"** - 48% of responses
- **"Reliable partner but limited innovation"** - 72% of responses
- **"Would consider alternatives for next purchase"** - 34% of responses
