# Brand Performance Measurement

**How we'll track brand transformation success**

::: info
**Brand KPIs:**
- **Awareness:** Unaided brand recognition (target: +40%)
- **Perception:** Brand attribute association (target: +50% for innovation)
- **Preference:** Consideration in purchase decisions (target: +35%)
- **Advocacy:** Net Promoter Score (target: +25 points)
- **Business Impact:** Marketing qualified leads (target: +30%)
:::

**Measurement Frequency:** Monthly tracking, quarterly deep dives

<<chart: bar>>
  data: [[25, 45, 30, 55, 35, 60]]
  labels: ["Brand Awareness", "Innovation Perception", "Purchase Consideration", "Customer Satisfaction", "Employee Advocacy", "Market Differentiation"]
  series: ["Target Improvement (%)"]
  options:
    responsive: true
    plugins:
      title:
        display: true
        text: "Brand Transformation Targets"

@notes:
- KPIs connect brand activities to business results
- Monthly tracking enables rapid course correction
- Targets are ambitious but achievable
- Business impact validates brand investment

